Interface INestedModel<M>

    public interface INestedModel<M>
extends IListModel<M>
    Extends the list model by adding support for nesting models within models.

        IListModel<M> getChildren(M parent)
        Returns the child list model given the parent. May return null. Note that the return type is not required to be a nested model, though it typically will be.
        Parameters:
